            <title><![CDATA[上海石化公司爆炸事故已造成一死一伤]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media figure-media-gallery figure-media-gallery-overlay js-figure-media-gallery js-figure-media-gallery-overlay">
         <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="article-rotator-img lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-06/china-fire-factory-industry-054212.jpg?VersionId=UkeI0MmjdyOAEy1OpvkmYXdHQ.D9rLVH&amp;itok=1-1Akxdl" alt="" data-caption="上海石化突发火情现场火势猛烈的航拍图。（法新社）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-06/china-fire-factory-industry-054212.jpg?VersionId=UkeI0MmjdyOAEy1OpvkmYXdHQ.D9rLVH&amp;itok=1-1Akxdl" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div>
