  </div>
         <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="article-rotator-img lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-06/xxjpsgc007108_20220618_pepfn0a001.jpg?VersionId=2Q2.2tiryD3JXlRLJLUKFxlTmAcT.nmG&amp;itok=M4-ZrjQF" alt="" data-caption="上海石化突发火情已导致一死一伤，图为无人机拍摄的救援现场。（新华社）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-06/xxjpsgc007108_20220618_pepfn0a001.jpg?VersionId=2Q2.2tiryD3JXlRLJLUKFxlTmAcT.nmG&amp;itok=M4-ZrjQF" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div>
